thread.title: Brian Michael Dougherty
thread.title_full: RushMyPassport.com reviewed by Brian Michael Dougherty

author: Brian Michael Dougherty
title: Brian Michael Dougherty
text: These guys did a great job. As long as you can read and follow instructions, you'll love this service. Even if you have trouble with directions, a representative will call you when you get to the appropriate step and make sure all your docs are in order. No waiting in line, the only big to-do on your part is to get a new photo taken. I recommend going to Fedex Office since you can get your photo taken and then mail your documents out right away.
